  <h1 class="article-headline">Your Creatine Is Working. Your Electrolytes Aren't. That Is Why Your Training Has Hit a Ceiling.</h1>
  <p class="article-deck">A peer-reviewed finding about how creatine enters muscle cells changes what every serious athlete should be doing on training day. Most are missing it.</p>
